Redshift, Time, Wavelength
public abstract class Quantity
extends AbstractScienceObjectNode

Quantity, abstract super class of double values that have measurement units

This code was developed by NASA, Goddard Space Flight Center, Code 588 for the Scientist's Expert Assistant (SEA) project for Next Generation Space Telescope (NGST). This class manages quantity values and supported units
